-- U.K. Retailer La Senza on Brink of Administration, Company Says
-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 2011-12-24T12:58:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-24/u-k-retailer-la-senza-on-brink-of-administration-company-says.html
La Senza, the U.K. lingerie retailer
owned by  Lion Capital LLP , said it has filed a notice of
intention to appoint administrators within the next 10 days.  La Senza is not currently in administration and no
administrators have yet been appointed, it said in an e-mailed
statement today.  The company is working with KPMG LLP to “explore all
options,” the statement added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in London at 
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
